  "detailed_description": "Cursors are easy to lose — especially in fast games or bright scenes. Customize and enhance your cursor in both games and Windows apps.<br><br>Ideal for MOBA, MMO, RPG, and ARPG games. Great for presentations, streaming, and everyday desktop use.<br><br>Let this cursor changer be your game changer! 😎<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Boost Visibility</h2>Make those tiny cursors large and colorful.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/c297f194cf9bb65d32eaea658b040e27.poster.avif?t=1774067730\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/c297f194cf9bb65d32eaea658b040e27.webm?t=1774067730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/c297f194cf9bb65d32eaea658b040e27.mp4?t=1774067730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enhance Existing Cursors</h2>Keep the original theme while enhancing cursors with size and glow.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/d00cb916c6d8c3a230000c126e1836da.poster.avif?t=1774067730\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/d00cb916c6d8c3a230000c126e1836da.webm?t=1774067730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/d00cb916c6d8c3a230000c126e1836da.mp4?t=1774067730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Add Effects</h2>Effects like zoom, cross, and halo improve clarity on busy screens.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/a315152524545e0a93b4bd5427b2a1cc.poster.avif?t=1774067730\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/a315152524545e0a93b4bd5427b2a1cc.webm?t=1774067730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/a315152524545e0a93b4bd5427b2a1cc.mp4?t=1774067730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Add Style</h2>Stylized and animated 3D cursor options.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/ff2c8d458f99cd30f0875f97bc86bc28.poster.avif?t=1774067730\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/ff2c8d458f99cd30f0875f97bc86bc28.webm?t=1774067730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/ff2c8d458f99cd30f0875f97bc86bc28.mp4?t=1774067730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Anywhere</strong>: Works in games and Windows apps.<br></li><li><strong>Size</strong>: Resize new and existing cursors.<br></li><li><strong>Colors</strong>: Wide range of colors, including inverted color.<br></li><li><strong>Effects</strong>: Add zoom, cross, halo, glow, and mirror.<br></li><li><strong>Presets</strong>: Quickly apply pre-assigned cursor sets.<br></li><li><strong>Create</strong>: Built-in editor supports basic and animated cursors.<br></li><li><strong>Fast</strong>: No bloat. No impact on performance.<br></li><li><strong>Variety</strong>: Includes many basic and 3D overlay cursors.<br></li><li><strong>Community</strong>: Share and download even more cursors via Steam Workshop.<br></li><li><strong>Fun</strong>: Jiggle physics!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Getting Started</h2>Hover a cursor you wish to change and hit <strong>CTRL ALT C</strong> to open the cursor selection UI. Then choose a new style, size, and color.<br><strong>PRO TIP:</strong> To make all cursors visible quickly, choose the special <strong>ALL</strong> cursor. Then increase the size or add glow.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Not a Cheat</h2>YoloMouse works like other accessibility tools. It does not modify games or provide gameplay advantages. It is widely whitelisted, code signed for security, and routinely tested against major titles. Always verify it complies with your game’s ToS before use.<br>",
  "about_the_game": "Cursors are easy to lose — especially in fast games or bright scenes. Customize and enhance your cursor in both games and Windows apps.<br><br>Ideal for MOBA, MMO, RPG, and ARPG games. Great for presentations, streaming, and everyday desktop use.<br><br>Let this cursor changer be your game changer! 😎<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Boost Visibility</h2>Make those tiny cursors large and colorful.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/c297f194cf9bb65d32eaea658b040e27.poster.avif?t=1774067730\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/c297f194cf9bb65d32eaea658b040e27.webm?t=1774067730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/c297f194cf9bb65d32eaea658b040e27.mp4?t=1774067730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enhance Existing Cursors</h2>Keep the original theme while enhancing cursors with size and glow.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/d00cb916c6d8c3a230000c126e1836da.poster.avif?t=1774067730\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/d00cb916c6d8c3a230000c126e1836da.webm?t=1774067730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/d00cb916c6d8c3a230000c126e1836da.mp4?t=1774067730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Add Effects</h2>Effects like zoom, cross, and halo improve clarity on busy screens.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/a315152524545e0a93b4bd5427b2a1cc.poster.avif?t=1774067730\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/a315152524545e0a93b4bd5427b2a1cc.webm?t=1774067730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/a315152524545e0a93b4bd5427b2a1cc.mp4?t=1774067730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Add Style</h2>Stylized and animated 3D cursor options.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/ff2c8d458f99cd30f0875f97bc86bc28.poster.avif?t=1774067730\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/ff2c8d458f99cd30f0875f97bc86bc28.webm?t=1774067730\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1283970/extras/ff2c8d458f99cd30f0875f97bc86bc28.mp4?t=1774067730\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Anywhere</strong>: Works in games and Windows apps.<br></li><li><strong>Size</strong>: Resize new and existing cursors.<br></li><li><strong>Colors</strong>: Wide range of colors, including inverted color.<br></li><li><strong>Effects</strong>: Add zoom, cross, halo, glow, and mirror.<br></li><li><strong>Presets</strong>: Quickly apply pre-assigned cursor sets.<br></li><li><strong>Create</strong>: Built-in editor supports basic and animated cursors.<br></li><li><strong>Fast</strong>: No bloat. No impact on performance.<br></li><li><strong>Variety</strong>: Includes many basic and 3D overlay cursors.<br></li><li><strong>Community</strong>: Share and download even more cursors via Steam Workshop.<br></li><li><strong>Fun</strong>: Jiggle physics!</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Getting Started</h2>Hover a cursor you wish to change and hit <strong>CTRL ALT C</strong> to open the cursor selection UI. Then choose a new style, size, and color.<br><strong>PRO TIP:</strong> To make all cursors visible quickly, choose the special <strong>ALL</strong> cursor. Then increase the size or add glow.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Not a Cheat</h2>YoloMouse works like other accessibility tools. It does not modify games or provide gameplay advantages. It is widely whitelisted, code signed for security, and routinely tested against major titles. Always verify it complies with your game’s ToS before use.<br>",
